Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.99,0:19:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.39,0:19:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢点儿啊 会被发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.11,0:19:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会被发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.81,0:20:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没水了 没水了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.52,0:20:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这都被看光了啊
