Dialogue: 0,1:52:29.64,1:52:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人要来了
Dialogue: 0,1:52:55.08,1:52:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这反而显眼了啊  糟透了
Dialogue: 0,1:53:11.83,1:53:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被完完全全地看到了
Dialogue: 0,1:53:15.12,1:53:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太爽了
Dialogue: 0,1:53:16.61,1:53:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,1:53:18.37,1:53:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,1:53:20.70,1:53:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧\N爽爆
Dialogue: 0,1:53:35.79,1:53:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,1:53:37.08,1:53:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿着零钱回去吧\N回去？
Dialogue: 0,1:53:39.73,1:53:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不叫店员可以吗
Dialogue: 0,1:53:41.82,1:53:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可现在这个样子..
Dialogue: 0,1:53:49.39,1:53:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊不行了 要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,1:54:16.88,1:54:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把我放下来
Dialogue: 0,1:54:22.57,1:54:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放我下来
Dialogue: 0,1:54:30.33,1:54:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想把脚放下去吗
Dialogue: 0,1:54:33.34,1:54:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要下去
Dialogue: 0,1:54:42.93,1:54:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫店员
Dialogue: 0,1:54:44.70,1:54:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店员不在的
Dialogue: 0,1:54:46.66,1:54:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等 叫店员
Dialogue: 0,1:54:48.45,1:54:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店员不在的
Dialogue: 0,1:54:52.48,1:54:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不行了 已经可以了
Dialogue: 0,1:55:43.65,1:55:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊真的不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:55:59.44,1:56:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行了不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:56:04.90,1:56:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 高潮了 不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:56:59.44,1:57:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受不了了
Dialogue: 0,1:57:25.37,1:57:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服 舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:57:40.48,1:57:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要高潮 高潮了
Dialogue: 0,1:58:34.84,1:58:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行了 不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:58:41.00,1:58:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:58:45.56,1:58:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(314,43)}（工作人员：在收银台那个样子会被怀疑哦）
Dialogue: 0,1:59:00.16,1:59:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不行了 真的
Dialogue: 0,1:59:07.13,1:59:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会成癖的 不行
Dialogue: 0,1:59:11.40,1:59:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太舒服了 真的舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:59:18.39,1:59:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后又要去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,1:59:22.34,1:59:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这回又是什么套路？
Dialogue: 0,1:59:26.50,1:59:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,1:59:32.83,1:59:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I社太会玩了
Dialogue: 0,1:59:34.88,1:59:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢 对不起呢
Dialogue: 0,1:59:40.26,1:59:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,零钱 零钱
Dialogue: 0,1:59:43.07,1:59:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(314,43)}（工作人员：刚才还了）
Dialogue: 0,1:59:48.15,1:59:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候 刚才？
Dialogue: 0,1:59:50.23,1:59:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(314,43)}（工作人员：你们俩进店之前）
Dialogue: 0,1:59:54.38,1:59:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们 是来干个啥啊？
Dialogue: 0,2:00:00.99,2:00:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没意义啊
Dialogue: 0,2:00:03.80,2:00:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被你们玩坏了
Dialogue: 0,2:00:09.64,2:00:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
